<div class="news-grid"><div class="news-card"><div class="news-thumb"><span class="news-date-mini">04 Dec</span>M</div><div class="news-body"><h4>Moi Senior School  Kabarak</h4><p>Holistic educational services in a learner-centred, co-educational Christian environment.</p><span class="news-author">By Notice Board</span></div></div><div class="news-card"><div class="news-thumb"><span class="news-date-mini">21 Apr</span>M</div><div class="news-body"><h4>MHSK Celebrates Successful First Term 2023</h4><p>Students reunited with their families after a term of blessings, challenges, and valuable lessons learned.</p><span class="news-author">By J. Mburu</span></div></div><div class="news-card"><div class="news-thumb"><span class="news-date-mini">19 Apr</span>W</div><div class="news-body"><h4>World Scholars Club  2024 Thailand Chapter</h4><p>MHSK students showcased academic prowess engaging with bright minds from around the world.</p><span class="news-author">By Webmaster</span></div></div><div class="news-card"><div class="news-thumb"><span class="news-date-mini">29 Mar</span>F</div><div class="news-body"><h4>Form Four Class of 2023 Sets 84-Point Target</h4><p>The Form Four class received exam results and set an ambitious target of A Plain 84 points.</p><span class="news-author">By J. Mburu</span></div></div><div class="news-card"><div class="news-thumb"><span class="news-date-mini">26 Mar</span>T</div><div class="news-body"><h4>Thanksgiving Day Festivities Honor 2022 KCSE Class</h4><p>A celebration honoring the exceptional performance of the 2022 K.C.S.E class  the Immanuels.</p><span class="news-author">By Webmaster</span></div></div><div class="news-card"><div class="news-thumb"><span class="news-date-mini">25 Mar</span>C</div><div class="news-body"><h4>Celebrating the Success of 2022 with God's Grace</h4><p>On the 16th Prize and Thanksgiving Ceremony, we give God all the glory.</p><span class="news-author">By CPA N. Kiptiony</span></div></div><div class="news-card"><div class="news-thumb"><span class="news-date-mini">25 Mar</span>W</div><div class="news-body"><h4>We Owe Our Success to Firm Christian Principles</h4><p>From 24 A's in 2021 to 33 A's in 2022  the Immanuels broke and set new records.</p><span class="news-author">By Rev. Dr. Ombati</span></div></div><div class="news-card"><div class="news-thumb"><span class="news-date-mini">25 Mar</span>A</div><div class="news-body"><h4>A Testimony of Exceptional KCSE Results</h4><p>Celebrating 351 candidates, the Immanuels, for maintaining MHSK's top position.</p><span class="news-author">By Mrs. M. Samo</span></div></div><div class="news-card"><div class="news-thumb"><span class="news-date-mini">25 Mar</span>A</div><div class="news-body"><h4>An Education Miracle: Journey of Faith and Perseverance</h4><p>MHSK's vision of holistic, Christian-based quality education continues to be realized.</p><span class="news-author">By Hon. G. K. Moi</span></div></div></div>
